# Configuration reference for the CDC stack. Copy to .env to source these.
# Every value here is a local-only dev default; nothing is hard coded in the
# worker. The worker reads the CDC_* variables below; the rest configure the
# docker-compose stack and the helper scripts.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Worker (the Go service in this repo). Each line shows the built-in default, so
# the worker runs with none of these set. Uncomment to override.
# Source of truth: internal/config/config.go.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Kafka source
# CDC_KAFKA_BROKERS=localhost:29092                      # comma separated host:port list
# CDC_KAFKA_GROUP=cdc-clickhouse-sink                    # consumer group id
# CDC_KAFKA_TOPICS=cdc.public.customers,cdc.public.orders # comma separated topics to consume

# ClickHouse sink
# CDC_CLICKHOUSE_DSN=clickhouse://default:@localhost:9000/cdc # native DSN
# CDC_CLICKHOUSE_DIAL_TIMEOUT=5s                         # bound the initial connect
# CDC_CLICKHOUSE_READ_TIMEOUT=30s                        # bound a stalled read or write; exceed worst batch latency

# Batching and flush
# CDC_BATCH_SIZE=1000                                    # rows buffered before a flush (must be > 0)
# CDC_FLUSH_INTERVAL=1s                                  # max time between flushes

# Retry and backpressure on a slow or paused ClickHouse
# CDC_RETRY_BASE=1s                                      # first flush retry backoff (doubles each attempt)
# CDC_RETRY_MAX=30s                                      # cap on the flush retry backoff

# Observability
# CDC_LAG_INTERVAL=5s                                    # how often to sample consumer lag into cdc_consumer_lag
# CDC_METRICS_ADDR=:9100                                 # host:port serving Prometheus /metrics
# CDC_LOG_LEVEL=info                                     # debug | info | warn | error

# Dead letter routing
# CDC_DLQ_TOPIC_SUFFIX=.dlq                              # appended to a source topic to form its dead-letter topic

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# docker-compose stack and helper scripts (local dev defaults).
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Kafka (host access via the PLAINTEXT_HOST listener)
KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP=localhost:29092

# Postgres
PGHOST=localhost
PGPORT=5432
PGUSER=cdc
PGPASSWORD=cdc
PGDATABASE=cdc
# DSN for the replication connection (replication=database)
DATABASE_URL=postgres://cdc:cdc@localhost:5432/cdc?sslmode=disable

# Kafka Connect (Debezium REST API)
CONNECT_REST_URL=http://localhost:8083

# ClickHouse
CLICKHOUSE_HOST=localhost
CLICKHOUSE_HTTP_PORT=8123
CLICKHOUSE_NATIVE_PORT=9000
CLICKHOUSE_USER=default
CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD=
CLICKHOUSE_DB=cdc
